T1  - Meaningful venturing: Examining how entrepreneurs generate meaning in life
AU  - Seyb, Stella
AU  - Shepherd, Dean A.
AU  - Maitlis, Sally
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 40
IS  - 5
SP  - 106526
PY  - 2025
